        {
            "title": "港股開跌135點   配股股份下挫   維立志博首掛飆逾倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數競價時段開跌135點0.53%，報25531點 ; 恒生科技指數開跌29點或0.51%，報5713點 ; 恒生國企指數開跌41點或0.45%，報9216點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市現成交.55億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"雲頂新耀2024年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/01952.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"雲頂新耀2024年度中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/01952.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">雲頂新耀2024年度中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雲頂新耀(01952) 折讓約10.12%配股，開跌5.87%，報73元，成交居首。科濟藥業(02171)預告虧損減逾77%，股價升2.83%，報25.4元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">OSL(00863)折讓15.34%配股，開跌10.68%，報15.72元，成交居第二位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首掛維立志博(09887)飆106.86%，報72.4元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長飛光纖(06869)挫5.66%，報20元，成交居第四位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三生製藥((01530)跌3.45%，報29.35元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120349-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e8%b7%8c135%e9%bb%9e-%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e4%b8%8b%e6%8c%ab-%e7%b6%ad%e7%ab%8b%e5%bf%97%e5%8d%9a%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be%e5%80%8d",
