        {
            "title": "科濟藥業預告半年虧損大減逾77%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科濟藥業(02171)公布，預期上半年淨虧損和經調整淨虧損按年減少，料淨虧損不超過約8000萬元(人民幣‧下同)，較去年同期虧損3.51億元大降77.21%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"科濟藥業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250725_fi_02171_1200.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"科濟藥業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250725_fi_02171_1200.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">科濟藥業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">經調整淨虧損(指不包括以股份為基礎的薪酬)的淨虧損不超過約7,500萬元，較去年同期為虧損3.42億元降78.07%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司稱虧損減少因CT053的商業化，及CT041的新藥申請(NDA)獲國家藥品監督管理局(NMPA)接納，此外研發開支大幅減少。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120314-%e7%a7%91%e6%bf%9f%e8%97%a5%e6%a5%ad%e9%a0%90%e5%91%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e5%a4%a7%e6%b8%9b%e9%80%be77",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/12/%E7%A7%91%E6%BF%9F%E8%97%A5%E6%A5%AD%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-25 09:15:29",
