        },
        {
            "title": "維立志博以35元定價　每手中籤率0.27%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生物科技企業維立志博(09887)公布招股結果，以發售價上限35元定價，集資淨額11.79億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：維立志博官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_LeadsBiolabs-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：維立志博官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_LeadsBiolabs-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：維立志博官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">股份公開發售部分超額認購3493.78倍，認購每手100股，中籤率0.27%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綜合3大暗盤場，輝立暗盤收70.05元，較招股價升35.05元或100.143%，未計手續費，一手100股帳面賺3,505元；耀才及富途暗盤同樣收69.75元，較招股價升34.75元或99.286%，未計手續費，一手100股帳面賺3,475元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120036-%e7%b6%ad%e7%ab%8b%e5%bf%97%e5%8d%9a%e4%bb%a535%e5%85%83%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9%e3%80%80%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%a4%e7%8e%870-27-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/09887.jpg.webp",
